					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Why would you want this, especially with these weird tempos? It is very easy to make triangle drums in Famitracker with the arpeggio sequence, the only problem is that you either have to make a drum instrument for every bass note, or just accept that drum pitch is changes along with notes.
<br />
<br />jsr was asked long ago for a 'fixed note' feature in the arpeggio sequences, this would make things like these much easier to handle, and he even implemented it in a WIP back then, but it was never included into any release. What a pity.</div>

					
